description:
Who's In Control?



Aired on 02/28/2011, Narrated by Jonathan Aris



On 25 February 2009, Turkish Airlines Flight 1951, a Boeing 737-800, is on approach to land at Schiphol in Amsterdam when it stalls and crashes 1.5 kilometers from the runway. Nine people, including the three cockpit crew, are killed.
